@startuml
actor Client
participant "Service A" as ServiceA #D3DAE7
participant "Service B" as ServiceB #D3DAE7

Client ->> ServiceA : GET /service-a/concept/1\nactivate ServiceA
deactivate ServiceA
return 301 Redirect: <b>/</b><i>service-b</i>/<u>concept</u>\n<font color=red>//(redirect)</font> //to//\nservice-b/concept/1 \nas redirectResponse 

note over redirectResponse 
 This response indicates that the resource has moved permanently to service-b. The client should update any bookmarks or links accordingly.
end note


Client ->> ServiceB : GET /service-b/concept/1\nactivate ServiceB
deactivate ServiceB
return 200 OK: &lt;object&gt;\nas objectReturn 


@enduml